description: Potential unsafe dataflow issue in `<blob_schema::BlobSchema<'static> as icu_provider::prelude::yoke::Yokeable<'a>>::transform_mut`
code_snippet:
#[derive(serde::Deserialize, yoke::Yokeable)]
#[yoke(prove_covariance_manually)]
#[cfg_attr(feature = "export", derive(serde::Serialize))]
#[derive(Debug, Clone)]
pub(crate) enum BlobSchema<'data> {
    V001(NeverSchema),
    V002(NeverSchema),
    V002Bigger(NeverSchema),
    #[serde(borrow)]
    V003(BlobSchemaV1<'data, Index16>),
    #[serde(borrow)]
    V003Bigger(BlobSchemaV1<'data, Index32>),
}
